Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.24,0:00:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.81,0:00:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for calling on you so early.\NI'm from the state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.55,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you Dr. Tenma?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.42,0:00:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.82,0:00:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, but were you at home\Nall night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.66,0:00:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I was out drinking\Nuntil it was nearly morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.13,0:00:46.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.16,0:00:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eisler Memorial Hospital's\NDirector Heinemann;
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.77,0:00:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief of Surgery, Dr. Oppenheim,\Nand Dr. Boyer are dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.50,0:02:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, no one except the police\Nare allowed at the scene of the crime!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.23,0:02:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, you are obstructing\Nthe operations of the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.70,0:02:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,The Press is not allowed
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.80,0:02:35.86,Default,,0,0,0,,inside the hospital!\N-Please don't do anything
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.94,0:02:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,to excite the patients!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.74,0:02:40.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it an accident?\NOr was it murder?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.31,0:02:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Three people died at the same time!\NOf course it was murder!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.15,0:02:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you from the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.65,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything\Nabout this incident?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.35,0:02:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of my way!\NLet me through!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.82,0:02:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! No one is allowed in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Kenzo Tenma of this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.72,0:02:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...go right ahead.\NHey! Don't push!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.26,0:02:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So, did you see anyone suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.86,0:03:00.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.\NNow is not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.00,0:03:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time...\N-Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.30,0:03:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma! The Director!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.30,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.40,0:03:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone, calm down!\NAre the emergencies taken care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.41,0:03:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,W-Well, even at this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.01,0:03:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,there's been no end\Nto the emergencies.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.51,0:03:15.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There are two patients\Nwaiting to be operated on...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.41,0:03:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand. I'll help out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.78,0:03:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care of the car accident victim\Nwith the brain contusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.72,0:03:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go to the X-ray Reading Room\Nto look at the x-rays first.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the other case?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.99,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,A patient who collapsed due to a stroke.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.82,0:03:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Doctor, will you help us\Nin our investigation?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Now is not the time...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that,\Nbut the initial investigation is vital!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.13,0:03:37.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know of anyone with a grudge\Nagainst the director and the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.53,0:03:39.50,Default,,0,0,0,,A grudge...?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.94,0:03:41.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You may consider your path\Nto becoming{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.84,0:03:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}the doctor you envisioned closed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...? Do you know something?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.05,0:03:50.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.25,0:03:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.55,0:03:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Trouble! Those kids...\NThe twin brother and sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.65,0:03:59.92,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't find them anywhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.50,0:04:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the sister's bed empty, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.30,0:04:15.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I looked!\NBut they're nowhere to be found...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.71,0:04:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What's going on...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.78,0:04:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What in the world has happened...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,...compassionately extended\Na helping hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.59,0:04:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,We will surely praise his lifetime\Nof achievements through eternity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Farewell Dr. Heinemann.\NRest in peace. Amen.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.91,0:04:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eva...\N-Eva.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know it's difficult,\Nbut pull yourself together...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.71,0:04:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.11,0:05:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Give back my father!\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.19,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just too much, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.96,0:05:14.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, she lived an easy life\Nas the director's daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now suddenly,\Nshe's just an ordinary person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:23.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It must be a big shock...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.71,0:05:25.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How can you say that\Nat a time like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.71,0:05:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, pardon me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.31,0:05:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.28,0:05:31.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Detective Visbaugh
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.71,0:05:34.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Of the Nordhein-Westfalen\NPolice Department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.58,0:05:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your efforts.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This was such a tragic incident...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me introduce you. This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.09,0:05:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I am Inspector Lunge of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.63,0:05:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I've heard rumors that\Nyou are a brilliant physician.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.23,0:05:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I've still got\Na long ways to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.44,0:05:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... Have you any idea\Nwhere the children are?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.58,0:06:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind them.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.58,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,We have determined what caused
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.98,0:06:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,the death of the director\Nand the other two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.18,0:06:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,We found a nitrate type poison\Nin their bodies.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.55,0:06:12.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Nitrates...\NThat means a muscular relaxant...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.29,0:06:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As expected of a doctor.\NYou are knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.89,0:06:17.66,Default,,0,0,0,,But how could something like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.16,0:06:19.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It was candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.10,0:06:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Candy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:25.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The same candy wrapper\Nwas found beside each body,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.90,0:06:28.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the same candy was found\Nin their stomachs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.31,0:06:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you have any idea\Nwhere the three of them
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.41,0:06:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,might get a hold of\Nsomething like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.91,0:06:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know anything about that.\NWhat about the search for the twins?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.98,0:06:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The BKA has\Ntaken over the investigation.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.32,0:06:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.93,0:06:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,This incident may have started
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.13,0:06:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,when the parents of those twins\Nwere shot and killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.13,0:06:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Their parents defected\Nfrom East Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and were killed by someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.84,0:07:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, the director and doctors\Nof the hospital
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.67,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,where the children were taken to\Nwere killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is also the possibility\Nthat this is political terrorism.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.08,0:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Those children might be\Nholding a major clue.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.98,0:07:13.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.\NPlease find them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.35,0:07:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,We will do our best.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.19,0:07:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.19,0:07:26.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Before the incident, the Director\Nremoved him from his position as Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Furthermore, the Director's daughter\Nbroke off her engagement to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.07,0:07:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But he was in a bar drinking\Nat the time of the incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:35.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He has an alibi...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.27,0:07:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Umm...\NMay I ask you something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.98,0:07:42.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you move\Nyour hand like that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:46.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NOh, I'm typing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.82,0:07:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.32,0:07:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm inputting all the information into\Nthe disk in my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.29,0:07:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,When I press the key\Nto extract the information...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.12,0:07:57.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. I still have\Na long ways to go."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.53,0:08:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what Dr. Tenma bashfully said\Nwhen I called him brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.87,0:08:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The police...? Do they suspect you\Nof doing something?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.77,0:08:15.34,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because there's enough evidence\Nfor me to be a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.35,0:08:17.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,They were quite persistent\Nwhen they questioned me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.49,0:08:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,When the dust from this thing settles,\NI think I'll go back to Japan...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.96,0:08:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What?\N-I came to Germany to do research,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.00,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but due to the recent chain of events,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.86,0:08:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I feel like I've gone back to saving lives,\Nthe true duty of a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.57,0:08:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't be so depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.87,0:08:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.21,0:08:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just so tired...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.01,0:08:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Your progress is favorable,\NMr. Buchner.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.48,0:09:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Tenma.\NDo you think I can work again?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.06,0:09:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.76,0:09:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,My store will go under\Nif I'm not there.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.73,0:09:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But you mustn't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.27,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go have a drink there\Nafter you're released.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.83,0:09:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be there to make sure\Nyou don't overdo things.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.37,0:09:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.84,0:09:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.87,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you were\Nleaving this hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.44,0:09:21.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.98,0:09:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.45,0:09:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.75,0:09:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't any\Ngood doctors like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.55,0:09:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't say you're quitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.35,0:09:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Buchner...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.20,0:09:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, the Chairman\Nis asking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.37,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The board is discussing who should\Nsucceed to the empty posts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:53.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Up until now, the Director's faction\Nhas filled the major positions...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.91,0:09:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There will be a considerable\Npurging of personnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.71,0:09:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The rumor is Dr. Eckner\Nis being transferred
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.28,0:10:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,to a small hospital in Bavaria.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.88,0:10:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so...\N-Umm, Dr. Tenma!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:07.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\N-No matter what the Chairman says,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,please don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.32,0:10:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.79,0:10:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Please don't leave this hospital!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.24,0:10:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.64,0:10:23.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll say it again.\NI am performance orientated.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.54,0:10:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Dr. Tenma, you are appointed to\NChief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.12,0:10:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What a life...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.72,0:10:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I went against the orders\Nof the Director,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.86,0:10:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}lost my position as Chief,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.66,0:10:46.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}and my engagement to Eva\Nwas dissolved.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.36,0:10:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}As soon as I decide to work\Nas a simple doctor{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.07,0:10:51.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}without any hope of promotion...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.61,0:11:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What a life!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.32,0:11:17.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry for calling you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.63,0:11:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you've been appointed\NChief of Surgery. That's very good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.33,0:11:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo... At my father's funeral,\Nyou tried to comfort me, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.44,0:11:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It made me happy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.15,0:11:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,A lot of things happened between us,\Nbut I'd like to try again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.36,0:11:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.83,0:11:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I was wrong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.56,0:11:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to try again!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.67,0:12:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.67,0:12:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Kenzo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.61,0:12:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient hospitalized\Nfor a spinal cord tumor...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:16.44,Default,,0,0,0,,His paralysis has accelerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand.\NI'll perform the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If you will, Chief of Surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Make the arrangements\Nfor the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.33,0:12:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly, when will this flood recede...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.54,0:12:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought the world would change
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,when the Berlin Wall came down\Nsix years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.94,0:12:39.27,Default,,0,0,0,,but nothing good has happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Even with the unification of Europe,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.94,0:12:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,hopeless people from all over\Ncome flowing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.05,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. There's been an increase in\Nunexplainable crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.95,0:12:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.32,0:12:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector, we've arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.76,0:12:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Both victims had their throats\Nslit open with a knife.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Their identities?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.56,0:13:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The Reichmanns of Stich Drive
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.30,0:13:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,They were murdered in their home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.87,0:13:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,We believe that they were\Nhidden in a closet,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.10,0:13:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,and their bodies floated out\Nbecause of the flood.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,A murder of a middle-aged couple.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.51,0:13:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,There have been four incidents\Nin Germany
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.18,0:13:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,over the past two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.71,0:13:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,All by the same method.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.62,0:13:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's probably a robber who targets\Nrich middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:26.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's too soon\Nto call them robberies.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,According to the data,\Nfor some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.09,0:13:31.49,Default,,0,0,0,,all of the couples\Ndid not have children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.93,0:13:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,This couple certainly\Ndid not have any children.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think there are\Ntoo many similarities
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.40,0:13:40.20,Default,,0,0,0,,to call them robberies?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.54,0:13:44.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But money and goods have been\Ntaken from all of the victims' homes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.94,0:13:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,All of them totaling very little.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.64,0:13:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,It would make sense\Nif a single perpetrator did it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.05,0:13:53.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you suggesting that\Nthere wasn't a single perpetrator?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:58.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Two of the homes had\Nextremely strong locks and alarms.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.85,0:14:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But the perpetrator opened them\Nand entered very easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.19,0:14:06.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, all the couples did not seem to\Nfight back when they were killed
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.00,0:14:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,and the neighbors did not hear\Nany noise at the time of the incidents.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.30,0:14:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think they were\Ntoo skillfully done
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.90,0:14:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,for it to have been done by\Na single individual?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:18.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.01,0:14:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Adolph Junkers, 32 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.68,0:14:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,He has been convicted twice\Nfor larceny.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.61,0:14:29.48,Default,,0,0,0,,His role was to open locks...\NIn other words, he's a lock picker.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:32.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He was seen near the scene
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.82,0:14:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,of three of the murders\Nof middle-aged couples.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.82,0:14:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Then did this man do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.39,0:14:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't say.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.03,0:14:44.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, that's the extent\Nof your work as state police.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest to the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.64,0:14:49.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh...yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.54,0:14:55.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.54,0:14:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,It didn't fly after all.\NI've never flown a kite before.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.02,0:15:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It almost went up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.78,0:15:04.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how was the girl last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.69,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,How was she?\NShe was a nice person.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.49,0:15:09.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, she's the daughter\Nof a director, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you just had dinner\Nand saw her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.30,0:15:16.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, there was an emergency call\Nduring dinner,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.30,0:15:17.93,Default,,0,0,0,,so I had to come back to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.10,0:15:23.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?! You'd better rethink that\Nall work and no play doctrine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.41,0:15:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to lose a great catch\Nand regret it some day!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Are you listening,\NChief of Surgery?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.71,0:15:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A kite...?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Chief.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.72,0:15:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that yours, Karl?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.22,0:15:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandpa gave it to me,\Nbut it just won't fly...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.49,0:15:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Could it be it's unbalanced?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.82,0:15:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, can you fly a kite?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.63,0:15:47.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it often during my childhood in\NJapan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.73,0:15:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Try holding it up high, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.70,0:15:53.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.04,0:15:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.\NNow...will it work?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.94,0:15:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Heave ho!\N-There!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.18,0:16:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.76,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It's flying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.89,0:16:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,If I were in his shoes,\NI'd have at least five lovers.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Honestly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.20,0:16:28.17,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Get well quickly\Nand fly it yourself, Karl.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.51,0:16:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.52,0:16:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's surgery is\Na parasellar meningioma extirpation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.92,0:16:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll proceed with\Na right pterional approach.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.39,0:16:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch closely. Chief Tenma\Nwill perform the surgery himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.83,0:16:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What a splendid operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.80,0:16:58.60,Default,,0,0,0,,He's hardly retracted the brain at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.40,0:17:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He truly is a surgical genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.87,0:17:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You residents should treat the brain\Nwith tender care.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.27,0:17:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Always keep this in mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.10,0:17:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.01,0:17:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,This is terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at the blood!\N-Ambulance! Call an ambulance!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.22,0:17:52.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I didn't do it!\NIt's not my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.92,0:17:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This man ran into the street suddenly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:00.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the patient?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.33,0:18:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.46,0:18:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,How is his condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I can't say...\NThere's nothing more we can do...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.87,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a material witness\Nin a certain case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.67,0:18:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,His testimony alone\Ncould solve a serial murder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.84,0:18:17.71,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't have him die.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.38,0:18:21.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But the patient is\Nin a very critical condition.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.58,0:18:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing more can be done\Nat our hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.55,0:18:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a terrific brain surgeon\Nat Eisler Memorial Hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If he came...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Brain surgeon...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.10,0:18:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean Dr. Tenma...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.17,0:18:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming all this way,\NDr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.81,0:18:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,How is the patient's condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.71,0:18:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,He is in a coma.\NAnd one of his pupils is dilated.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.91,0:18:51.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been a long time, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.88,0:18:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...I'm sorry,\Nbut who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:19:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been nine years.\NNot since the Director's funeral...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.22,0:19:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If I'm not mistaken,\Nyou're with the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.26,0:19:04.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Inspector Lunge.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.96,0:19:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Please make this operation a success\Nfor the sake of the BKA.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.27,0:19:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The patient has to live.\NHe holds the key to solving a big case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't operate\Nfor the sake of the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.18,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I do it for the sake of the patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.28,0:19:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I have an operation to perform...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I hear you've become\Nthe Chief of Surgery, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.29,0:19:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been very successful...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.16,0:19:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there a problem?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.59,0:19:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No. At your age,\Nit's quite an accomplishment.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.10,0:19:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Aren't you in line\Nto become the next Director?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.96,0:19:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No, that would be\Na long way off for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,About the murders\Nat the Eisler Memorial Hospital...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.00,0:19:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,There is very little evidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.31,0:19:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The investigation\Nhas been extremely difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.71,0:19:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The only clue is the poisoned candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.71,0:19:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,The methodology means\Nit is an intelligent crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.52,0:20:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,An intelligent crime means
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,the victim and the assailant\Nhave some sort of interests at stake
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.29,0:20:08.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you trying to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.12,0:20:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No, excuse me. In this business,\NI'm constantly thinking like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.83,0:20:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,In any case, rest assured.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.93,0:20:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,All the cases I've ever handled\Nhave been solved.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.24,0:20:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Every single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.84,0:20:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope so.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.85,0:20:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We will perform a craniotomy\Nto remove the hematoma.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.85,0:20:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,We must hurry. There is the danger\Nof the brain hernia worsening.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.83,0:20:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how you look at it,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.93,0:20:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,only one person greatly benefited from\Nthe Eisler Memorial Hospital murders.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.27,0:20:59.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That is you, Dr. Tenma.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.71,0:21:08.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for taking the trouble\Nto come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.92,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Not at all. How has\Nthe patient been doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.82,0:21:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,He's conscious,\Nbut his right pupil remains dilated...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.79,0:21:17.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And he has some paralysis\Non the left side.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:22.16,Default,,0,0,0,,He's started rehab already, hasn't he?\NThe paralysis should go away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.73,0:21:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,He's recovering normally.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the police will want to see him,\Nbut please refuse for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But, that detective, Lunge,\Nis so persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.54,0:21:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, the patient's recovery\Nis most important.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.15,0:21:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,How are you feeling, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.86,0:21:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Junkers, do you recognize me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.73,0:21:53.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you see this finger?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.07,0:21:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it? Can you answer me?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.91,0:22:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.37,0:22:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.78,0:22:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that, Mr. Junkers?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.38,0:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.18,0:22:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming...? What's coming?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.89,0:22:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.23,0:22:28.16,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster...is coming...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.03,0:22:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The monster?!
